<template>
  <Modal>
    <template #title>
        Delete Todo!!
    </template>
    <template #body>
        sure delete?
    </template>
    <template #footer>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" @click="onClose">Close</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger" @click="onDelete">Delete</button>
    </template>
  </Modal>
</template>

<script>
import Modal from '@/components/Modal.vue';
export default {
    components: {
        Modal
    },
    setup(props, { emit }){
        const onClose = () => {
            emit('close');
        }
        const onDelete = () => {
            emit('delete')
        }   
        return{
            onClose,
            onDelete
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
